failed.title: You should not change or delete the existing elements in the head tag
The styles.css file should be empty
Do not use any inline styles, just use the bootstrap classes for styling
The Jumbotron should be inside the first row
The Jumbotron first element should be an H1 tag
The Jumbotron second element should be a P tag
The Jumbotron third element should be an anchor tag with a large blue button class
The 3 columns should contain an H2, a p and a button
The 3 columns should contain the class col-4
